-- China Construction Bank to Open 100 Rural Branches, 21st Herald Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-08T23:48:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/china-construction-bank-to-open-100-rural-branches-21st-herald-reports.html

          
          
             China Construction Bank Corp. plans
to open 100 rural bank branches by the end of next year, the
21st Century Business Herald reported, citing an unidentified
person close to the bank.  
 The plan has received approval from the State Council, the
report said.  
          
          


  


        